source.a2016e17: # RNN * RNN(Recurrent Neural Network) is a NN type that can **remember the past**. It **cannot remember everything** but this memory **enables them to predict future or continuation of a thing**. For example: Lets say we have a text that says: "I have sauce and pasta, I will make a ...". RNN can complete that text: "I have sauce and pasta, I will make a **sauced pasta**".
